Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who was waiting in the pouring rain at the tennis court for 4 hours!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is changing into dry clothes\Nright now and will then come here.{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush and just spit it out.{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is coming here on a bike in this rain!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell's with you?{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jeet Kune Do...{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He dodged it!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you down!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that person! The one\NSonoko wanted you to meet!{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{18}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{19}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{20}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door of the toilet was\Nunlocked, so I opened it...{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And inside...{Retracted from the previous Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{25}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{26}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Suspect is Makoto Kyogoku\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He definitely drowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coroner just informed me that water had\Naccumulated in his respiratory tracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even assuming that he\Nwas knocked out with a stun gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,drowning such a fit man\Nwithout tying him up somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you need two\Nor three people for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it were a karate master,\None would be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you still\Nsuspecting Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Not particularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was also informed that there's pressure marks\Nin the form of a line on the corpse's lower abdomen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the lower abdomen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... There were no such marks on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So maybe the killer carried the corpse by the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would need to have quite powerful arms for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a karate master, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I said for example. For example.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, you said that the victim had a lot of\Nthings going on earlier. What did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:56.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sunami Masaki (29)\NMiddle School Science Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:56.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Michiko Mon'na (30)\NMiddle School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:55.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and my little\Nsister were planning to marry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,but his father was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems his parents had already\Narranged for him to marry another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When they found out,\Nthe two of them were shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they had considered\Neloping at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end, only my sister killed herself\Nby jumping into the ocean to drown...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they talk to you about eloping?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I got an e-mail from my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The two of us are going away together", it said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got that mail as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she and I were classmates and best friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was from that point on, wasn't it? That Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}\Nwould start getting violent when drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's why, when he\Nwoke up while we were bowling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably got into a fight\Nwith someone and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say. Do you come often to this bowling alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since the girl who passed away loved bowling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, it rained the last\Nfew times we came here as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a wet towel and four strange empty cans\Nin the bin next to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Empty cans?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All four are burned around the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is because someone\Nused them as an ashtray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But the smell of kerosene comes from inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait... Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Forensics Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you check it out? That shelf over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no! Kids should be over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Uncle Kogoro said that there might be\Nsomething in the spare toilet paper roll(s)...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what an obstinate boy... But, well, if you say\Nthat Sleeping Kogoro asked you to check it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burn marks on the ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Take some pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So it's like that after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:07.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That explains why the lower part of the wall\Ninside the toilet was curiously wet like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no doubt about it!\NThat person was the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:16.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"It seems like he has\Nalso arrived at the truth..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:23.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"But whether or not our deductions are the same...\NLately I've been losing confidence in that regard..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh! That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Who is he?", is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I guess that was to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh! It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"If it's him there's no problem", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fight! It was a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drunken victim who was sleeping in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,woke up, went to some bar to start drinking again\Nand there it came to a fight with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was taken somewhere and killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when you and your companions\Nwent around the bars to look for the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,did not everyone say they had not seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were probably just playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the bar's reputation would suffer if it came out\Nthat customers had been brawling there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why was the killer carrying a stun gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, where and why\Ndid he drown the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's absolutely no reason for the killer\Nto leave the corpse in the toilet on the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the victim had been sleeping in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, the victim, Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was brought to the car on this\Nparking lot by Masaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to sleep off his inebriation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And before Mon'na{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} went\Nto check on him about an hour later,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he must have woken up and left the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while we went looking for\NTamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} in various bars
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after hearing that he had disappeared...\NAfter getting into an argument with someone somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was drowned, and before we\Ncame back to the parking lot again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was placed inside the toilet on the\Nparking lot. There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that the person who was taking a nap\Nin the car on that same parking lot the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this karate guy is suspicious as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But considering the fact that\Nthe killer used a stun gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's completely innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm saying you should\Nhurry up and go around the bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to properly question people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The preparations for the experiment are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the forensics people said that\NDetective Mouri needed it to solve the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that you had given your permission, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But according to the forensic scientist, this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, let's go take a look! I love experiments!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would some shrimp who's in the first year of grade\Nschool even have done an experiment before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but he might have done so at Doc's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go and find out what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"If it's him there's no problem"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}know this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The area around the toilet is totally flooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but... You ordered us to do so, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said we should put a towel over the drain\Nto hold back the rain water and let it accumulate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, since the ground is inclined\Nhere due to land subsidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain that fell until a little\Nwhile ago has accumulated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But like this, the valuable\Ncrime scene is completely ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We transferred the toilet box with the corpse\Nsomewhere else and are in the process of examining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a different toilet box.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was also done on Detective Mouri's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I've said before, I didn't say any such—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Dad?! There's water gathered there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it matter if my pants get wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it helps me verify this trick, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W=When you say trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be... that the victim was drowned\Nusing this accumulated rain water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it takes quite a while\Nfor this much rain water to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, even if the victim\Nwas knocked out by a stun gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you would need quite a bit of force to drown\Na grown man in this water without binding him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the killer must have been\Nsomeone rather strong after all, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nisn't like that, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you don't need to be\Nstrong in order to use this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer locked up the victim in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the victim was drowned\Nwithout being touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But seeing is believing,\Nso why don't we try it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether we can actually drown\Nsomeone inside that toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Inspector Yamamura,\Nyou'll be the guinea pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I asked the forensics people\Nto prepare some oxygen for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that an oxygen flask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, tomboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can help set up the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also understood the trick that was used, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First the victim is placed in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the vents at the back of the box are sealed with tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, we fill four cans with kerosene\Nand stuff some paper into the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After lighting the paper up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we place the cans on the rack inside the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, we only need to close the door\Nand seal the openings with tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And how does he drown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water doesn't reach farther than my ankles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could someone drown like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's getting rather hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?!\NWhat just happened inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then... Why don't you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you any idea what you\Nput me through, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could've drowned, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But why was there so much water inside the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the pressure inside the toilet fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you never seen that science experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one where you place a burning\Ncandle in a bowl filled with water,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put a beaker over the candle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when the flame goes out, more and\Nmore water gets sucked into the beaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same thing happened here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cans burn on the rack inside the airtight toilet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the air becomes warmer and expands...\NThe amount of oxygen is reduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when the flames go out the air\Nbecomes cooler and contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to fill that space, the rain water that accumulated is\Nsucked into the toilet through the lower vents. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Science teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masaki Sunami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First you brought Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} to the\Ntoilet box while walking him to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying something like "I forgot my keys,\Nso please shelter from the rain inside the toilet."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once he was inside, you knocked\Nhim out with a stun gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and passed a piece of string through his belt,\Nwhich you then tied to the joints of the toilet seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,preventing Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} from standing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you placed the four cans filled with\Nkerosene on the rack inside the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and locked the door using a padlock,\Nputting up the "out of order" sign at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards you only had to seal\Nthe vents on the back with tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and close off the drain with a towel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the rain water would\Nstart to accumulate, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told Mon'na{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} that he had\Nfallen asleep in the car, an easy lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and waited for the rain water to gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after a while, Mon'na{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, who worries easily,\Nwent to go look after Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, all according to plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even if she hadn't done\Nso out of her own volition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you probably intended go check on him\Nyourself while inviting her along...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you had thought, she came back and\Nannounced that Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} wasn't in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And once everyone started\Nsearching the parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you confirmed that enough\Nrain water had gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,removed the sign stuck to the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lit the cans that were placed on the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sealed the door with tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards the rain water\Nwas sucked into the toilet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just like it happened in the experiment,\Ndrowning Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were going around the bars with Mon'na{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, effectively giving you an alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you returned to the parking lot again,\Nremoved the towel from the drain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the accumulated water could drain off,\Npeeled off all of the tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,threw the cans into the bin and cut the string\Nthat had been fastened to Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in order to hide the fact that\Nthe toilet had been filled with water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you placed new toilet paper rolls on the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before giving off a scream, as though\Nyou had just discovered the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For this trick to work it is important\Nto find the body as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the discovery is delayed, the time span\Nfor the estimated time of death widens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nullifying the painstakingly created alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the murderer must be the person\Nwho discovered the body —\hin other words, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are also the only one who could have created\Nthe time for the rain water to accumulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The forensics people are probably retrieving\Nthe tape with your fingerprints right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it wasn't in the rubbish bin,\Nyou must have flushed it down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And peeling off tape is rather\Ndifficult with gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This must be some sort of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Sunami has no reason\Nat all to kill Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man let my best friend die without doing anything.\NWhat better motive could there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-When you say best friend...\NAre you talking about my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, your sister, who had\Nplanned to marry that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my sister threw herself\Noff a cliff by the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was even a suicide note...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wrote a mail beforehand, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying "The two of us are going away together"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mail wasn't about eloping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a double suicide note, saying the two of them\Nwere going away to the next world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that man suddenly\Nbecame afraid of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and without trying to help your\Ndrowning sister, he left that cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was drunk that man\Ntold me so without inhibition...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying "I'm a hopeless coward" while crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even though he's like that...\NMy best friend loved him to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I helped him get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Into the water where she was waiting for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to look for the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I thought you didn't know who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it appeared that the\Nkiller was exceptionally strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured I would be able to\Nfeel his killing intent if I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if possible you wanted to\Nhave a fight with him, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, that might have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was simply looking for a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I've come to expect of you, Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solving the case so superbly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As expected of the true me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, but, that experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That fumbler, he's completely fallen\Nback to his old way of talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, she took all the good parts though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta change your pants\Nquickly or you'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, you were just doing your\Ndeductions while sitting in a puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's this? I'm soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Uncle, you did say "What does\Nit matter if my pants get wet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I... say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Super cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A message... From my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, I see... So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A PS...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"PS: Have you already met the wizard?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You could say so...
